Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
