Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102040,103166}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105001,107211}Hey, Ruby! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108671,109922}Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109922,112842}Meimi! Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:00.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119515,120850}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.85,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:123186,126856}Her True Character Revealed!\NMeimi's Critical Moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130485,132612}Sawatari. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133154,136783}Sorry about the last contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:21.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136783,141245}I want to start taking\Nphotos now for the next contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141245,143706}You're beautiful\Nin your school uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143706,147001}but you're also beautiful\Nwhen you're playing at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147001,147794}You're so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148670,150088}Senorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:35.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152340,155635}I'm leaving now.\NSee you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:54.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170066,174112}May I have a second of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174487,177115}Neverland Toy Shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:03.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177573,183079}Oh, it's the big toy store that\Njust opened on Second Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:08.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183871,188543}Did you know that there used to be\Na small toy store there, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189377,190795}Now I remember…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192422,195717}There was a very big tree there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195717,197009}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:22.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197844,202265}Until a year ago\Nthat was my father's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203766,207603}But it was taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207603,209939}We had to let the store go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218406,221617}And you came here for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:47.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223536,227039}No, I'm all right with the store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:51.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227039,231419}But I need your help with the tree\Nin front of our old store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:55.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231419,235381}The tree is still there\Nas the new store's display.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:02.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237133,242263}Recently I remembered that\NI left my music box in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242263,244390}I thought that I had lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244390,247268}Why did you leave it\Nin such a high place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248227,251272}When I was a child,\NI often climbed the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252982,256152}Recently I was going through\Nmy grandfather's belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256152,259864}Then I suddenly\Nremembered my music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259864,261699}It must be in the hole in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263075,265077}It's very important to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265077,268289}Yes. My grandfather gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:34.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269499,274837}It's a souvenir from my grandfather's\Ntrip to Switzerland when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288226,292188}Since that time, he was\Ninterested in music boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293314,297527}Immediately after coming back,\Nhe opened his toy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:04.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299153,304075}At the time, I didn't know the story\Nbehind the music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:09.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304867,309080}But that was my favorite\Nthing when I was child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309956,313918}I always had it with me,\Neven when playing or sleeping…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313918,318047}But I misplaced it\Nwithout even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:23.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318798,323219}So she wants to get it back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:28.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323219,328307}She says it's a beautiful music box which plays\Nthe hymn, "Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:35.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328307,335857}Naomi has asked the owner many times\Nto return her music box…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337733,339026}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339569,342738}We just opened the store.\NWe can't take on extra stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:48.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343990,348035}To others, it may be\Njust a music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348035,351706}But to me it's something\Nvery important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353124,354417}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354417,356711}This is a job for\Nthe phantom thief St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360423,362550}Hey, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362550,363718}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363718,364886}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364886,366679}– Hey, good morning!\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366679,368180}You have something in your hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370766,372685}This method is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374395,377106}"Tomorrow night,\NI'm going to Neverland
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377106,380151}to retrieve a music box which plays\N'Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee'."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380526,381944}St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:22.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381944,382987}A note of warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385406,388367}As usual, you're caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389076,390077}Saruwatari…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390536,393080}Are you challenging me\Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394373,396584}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397668,401005}Don't touch that!\NIt's a special photo of Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401589,403507}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408888,410765}Oh, it's just a regular…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411682,415645}Hey, Asuka Jr.!\NDon't touch it with your dirty hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415645,417480}What's this thing with Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418648,420566}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:04.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420566,424487}Unfortunately, I only have eyes\Nfor the beautiful Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426322,429283}Are you even listening to me?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432787,434789}{\i1}I've seen this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439210,441504}{\i1}If I remember correctly,\NI saw it at that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441504,443506}{\i1}It was with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446258,447259}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450262,451764}What…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453474,454892}What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460481,461524}{\i1}Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466362,467530}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470324,473661}Give it back, Asuka!\NI took that picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474161,477665}Haneoka!\NWhat is that next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483963,485631}{\i1}What should I tell him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486007,487508}That's a…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488426,491429}That's a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491429,492388}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:18.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494390,498102}What do you want to do\Nwith the stuffed porcupine, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498728,500021}It's a stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500021,501814}Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501814,504567}I know I have to grow out\Nof collecting stuffed animals, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505151,507319}You're in trouble, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507319,508612}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508988,510823}Wait! Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510823,512033}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516037,517455}If you're too pushy, she'll hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518748,520583}How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524295,526839}Thank you, Seira.\NYou saved me in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526839,530092}Anyway, now is\Nthe time to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531177,535014}In school, let's maintain\Nthat Ruby is a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535014,535931}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535931,539018}And Asuka Jr. is still\Nhaving doubts about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539018,541062}Don't let him provoke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541854,543647}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543647,546567}Mice is the plural form of mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:11.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547318,551030}Now I'll read an excerpt\Nfrom Aesop's Fables.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551030,553324}"The Town Mouse\Nand the Country Mouse."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553324,556118}– Please listen to me carefully.\N– Meimi, I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:20.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556118,560289}I'm going to buy concert tickets\Nthis afternoon. Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561999,563209}{\i1}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564293,567755}{\i1}Could you be…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579433,581936}I don't know why\Nthis bothers you so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:46.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581936,586232}but do you want me to find out\Nif this is a real stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587775,589527}Sawatari, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590111,591779}…are nicer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592822,595741}Of course! We're classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596325,597743}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598077,600955}For that reason,\Nplease go out on a date with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600955,602498}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602498,604083}For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:10.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604708,610798}I want to take another picture\Nof you with the stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610798,612967}May I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613384,615344}Uh, I'm sorry, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615344,617930}Well, how about after school\Ntomorrow? All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620599,622351}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623602,626522}Which would you like,\Nrice balls or sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626522,628899}In the middle of this mess,\Nyou're talking about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629233,630442}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630442,632653}Of course I'm talking about\Nthe snack for tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632653,634864}You'll get hungry during\Ntomorrow night's surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636282,637908}Which one would you like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638659,640828}Neither! Give me some space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649086,651046}– Sawatari!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651922,654758}I'll go on the date after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654967,656510}Me… Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656510,658262}What?! It's my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658846,659930}{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665853,667021}{\i1}Oh, Lord…
Comment: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:08.02,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:668022,668022}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:13.02,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:673027,673027}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678240,681285}That's why I'm asking\Nfor forgiveness! Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681285,682620}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682620,684955}Your date and warning note\Nare on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685289,687041}It will work out somehow…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688250,690920}We were able to manage Ruby\Nwithout too much trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692004,694173}But I was careless, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694173,697426}There are stuffed porcupines…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697426,700721}Yeah, I have seen one\Nat a toy store before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:44.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700721,704391}It was a stuffed animal with a music box,\Nand it looks exactly like Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705476,709188}We can buy it and fool Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709188,710022}That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710022,711857}The music that plays is also…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712233,714318}"Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:58.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714318,718948}All right! Then I'm going to get\Nthe stuffed animal that looks like Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719615,722952}Actually, I checked earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723827,725955}It's out of stock now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730000,731377}Out of stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731585,734129}What should I do, Seira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734129,736632}There's no other way now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:30.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746267,750062}Ruby, could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754358,757444}Can you pretend to be a stuffed animal\Nfor the rest of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761282,762950}– Eimi!\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762950,764660}It's another peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764660,766120}Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.08,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:772876,774086}{\fad(500,0)}Trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774795,777589}Are you going to take\NRuby to school, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777798,780092}What? Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780926,783929}Well, Ruby seems\Nto have caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783929,786724}So I'm thinking of\Ndropping her off at the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789935,793147}That's all! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800070,802906}I managed to fool Dad and Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802906,805326}The harder part is coming up, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806910,808829}Let's hang in there all day today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818964,820799}One hour later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823927,826930}Three hours later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826930,828766}After school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839360,841195}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842071,843530}Where should we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848911,851121}{\i1}Is it going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:17.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854333,857086}Well, in our store,\Na music box with the hymn…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:21.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857336,861048}"Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861048,863550}is only sold with this item.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867471,869014}That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:33.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869390,873477}Yes. They're out of stock now and\Nwe have only this one for display.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:47.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883737,887658}{\i1}I see. So this is the one\Nthat St. Tail is targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889618,892413}Whew! It's a big toy store!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894415,897751}{\i1}That must be the tree\Nwhere the music box is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902381,903715}Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903715,904925}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904925,906844}Right now, we're having\Na grand opening sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907052,910305}So we can't close the store,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912599,915811}Well, I would like\Nto borrow something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.31,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:915811,917312}Employee Locker Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916770,919815}Shoot! Why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921442,923026}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924319,925821}Asuka Jr.!\N…what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932077,935372}This time your strategy is to disguise yourself\Nand then catch her, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935372,936832}Aha! Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936832,938459}{\i1}Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944923,946800}Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946800,948886}Sawatari! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950262,952431}I don't know any fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952431,954433}It's me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954433,957436}What are you doing\Nin that costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:02.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957436,962649}I… I am doing this…\Nin order to catch St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:07.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962649,967112}It doesn't really matter.\NBut you do look good in that costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967112,968947}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968947,972326}Enough about me!\NWhat can you report?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974286,976497}It's a stuffed animal. Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:21.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977706,981668}Really, you can't see past\NHaneoka, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981668,982794}I'll look into it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994431,996850}What's the matter, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996850,999269}As you can see, it's a fox.\NCome on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006902,1010280}{\i1}I just want to know\Nif that's really a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010280,1011990}{\i1}That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012866,1014201}Oops. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024753,1026004}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026004,1028173}A smiling fox is\Nfalling down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031718,1032636}Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032928,1035931}{\i1}I knew the way\Nthat fox fell was familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035931,1037432}{\i1}It's like I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041228,1042563}This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043021,1046108}Oh, no! I've caught a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051238,1053031}{\i1}What should I do, Seira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060038,1062416}Here she comes! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062416,1064710}I won't let you escape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065752,1067212}Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070924,1072676}She disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072676,1073760}Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:18:00.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075304,1080851}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085731,1086857}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089192,1090527}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092487,1095198}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110547,1113300}She just appeared\Non top of the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118680,1120766}For me, it was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122142,1125812}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126897,1129316}Good evening, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129316,1130901}I'm sorry for disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130901,1133528}Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140452,1141495}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143372,1146041}Show…
